ry-Matt-LeBlanc-Courteney-Cox-David-Schwimmer-Jennifer-Aniston-and-Lisa-Kudrow-Photo-by-Jim-Smeal_Ron-Galella-Collection-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Matthew-Perry-Matt-LeBlanc-Courteney-Cox-David-Schwimmer-Jennifer-Aniston-and-Lisa-Kudrow-Photo-by-Jim-Smeal_Ron-Galella-Collection-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Matthew-Perry-Matt-LeBlanc-Courteney-Cox-David-Schwimmer-Jennifer-Aniston-and-Lisa-Kudrow-Photo-by-Jim-Smeal_Ron-Galella-Collection-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Matthew-Perry-Matt-LeBlanc-Courteney-Cox-David-Schwimmer-Jennifer-Aniston-and-Lisa-Kudrow-Photo-by-Jim-Smeal_Ron-Galella-Collection-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Matthew-Perry-Matt-LeBlanc-Courteney-Cox-David-Schwimmer-Jennifer-Aniston-and-Lisa-Kudrow-Photo-by-Jim-Smeal_Ron-Galella-Collection-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Matthew-Perry-Matt-LeBlanc-Courteney-Cox-David-Schwimmer-Jennifer-Aniston-and-Lisa-Kudrow-Photo-by-Jim-Smeal_Ron-Galella-Collection-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794896" class="wp-caption-text"> (LR) 《老友记》演员阵容 – 马修·佩里、马特·勒布朗、柯特妮·考克斯、大卫·休默、詹妮弗·安妮斯顿和丽莎·库卓 – 图片来源：Jim Smeal/Ron Galella Collection via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> 9 月，马克·查韦斯 (Mark Chavez) 博士被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/doctor-charged-in-matthew-perrys-death-expected-to-plead-guilty-today-3799088">指控与该演员的死亡有关，并承认密谋分发氯胺酮罪</a>。另外两人——佩里的助手肯尼思·岩间和朋友埃里克·弗莱明—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-update-actors-manager-reportedly-retired-after-his-death-3790234">已经承认参与了</a>这位<i>《老友记》</i>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-dead-54-friends-tributes-3524335">吸毒过量的致命事件</a>。</p><p>检察官对岩间、弗莱明和查韦斯提出了较轻的指控，以换取他们的合作，因为他们正在追捕他们认为对佩里之死负有更大责任的其他人，即萨尔瓦多·普拉森西亚博士和贾斯文·桑加—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/who-is-jasveen-sangha-the-ketamine-queen-accused-of-supplying-matthew-perry-3784599">所谓的“氯胺酮女王”</a> ——据称他们向佩里提供了氯胺酮。与氯胺酮。</p><p>桑加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ketamine-queen-lawyer-says-they-never-met-matthew-perry-despite-being-accused-of-supplying-him-with-drugs-3793086">不认罪，并声称她从未见过佩里</a>。普拉森西亚博士还对在佩里去世前一个月非法向佩里出售氯胺酮的罪名表示不认罪。两者均将于 2025 年 3 月接受审判。</p><p>与此同时，安妮斯顿在最近接受昆塔·布伦森采访时被问及佩里去世后观看<em>《老友记》的</em>感受时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/jennifer-aniston-brought-to-tears-by-friends-interview-question-3763624">，她流下了眼泪</a>。</p><p>在最近的该剧 30 周年纪念日上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/courteney-cox-says-she-cant-imagine-friends-reboot-while-celebrating-shows-30th-anniversary-3796092">考克斯表示她“无法想象”重启《<i>老友记</i>》会成功</a>。 “尝试重做任何事情都很困难，”她说。 “对于这个团体来说，任何前面带有‘re’的东西……我认为这都很特别。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-lisa-kudrow-surprise-fans-at-the-friends-couch-at-warner-bros-lot-3825069">《观看丽莎·库卓在华纳兄弟的《老友记》沙发上为粉丝带来惊喜》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
